column1: Ant x Plant association matrix from Blüthgen et al. (2004) Oikos 106: 344-358. Counts of ant colonies attending extrafloral (EFN) and floral nectaries (FN) are provided. Independent abundance estimates for ant colonies based on sugar bait experiment, see Blüthgen & Fiedler (2004) J. Anim. Ecol. 73: 155-166. Ants with abundance = 0 were not recorded during bait experiments. For plants, number of plant individuals on which any insect were recorded on nectaries given as abundance estimate. Plant life forms: cl = climber, he = herb, sh = shrub, tr = tree, pa = palm.
